{
  "texts": [
    "Reminiscence therapy can enhance emotional wellbeing and cognitive function, as it encourages communication and the recollection of personal histories.",
    "Carós et al. (2020) built Elizabot, a language model that mimics a reminiscence therapist.",
    "It consists of two components, a model that analyzes and captions the images used in the therapy, and a model for simple conversations.",
    "The authors received positive feedback from PwD trialing its use.",
    "Similarly, Morales-de-Jesús et al. (2021) implemented an automated reminiscence model."
  ]
}